   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:30:26,792:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:   │ xyz = (0.038, 0, 0)
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:30:26,793:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:   ↓
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:30:26,793:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 右手首ピッチ
   DEBUG: 2026-06-17 16:30:26,793:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:   │ xyz = (0.046, 0, 0)
